<lb ed="P" n="0702b04"/>
<lb ed="P" n="0702b05"/><cb:juan fun="close" n="21"><cb:jhead>首楞嚴經義海卷第二十一　牧一</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="P" n="0702b06"/><cb:div type="w"><head>音釋</head>
<lb ed="P" n="0702b07"/><cb:div type="note"><entry><form>樺</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pP168p0702b0702" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">胡化切木名</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>磣</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pP168p0702b0708" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">初朕切磣毒也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>僇</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pP168p0702b0715" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">力竹切殺也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>佇</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pP168p0702b0721" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">丈<term rend="no_nor">吕</term>切久立也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="P" n="0702b08"/><entry><form>瞪瞢</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pP168p0702b0803" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">瞪澄應切瞢莫亘切瞪瞢直視也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>刳</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pP168p0702b0817" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">空胡切虛其中也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form><g ref="#CB08016">󱽐</g></form><cb:def><p xml:id="pP168p0702b0825" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">兖角
<lb ed="P" n="0702b09"/>切卵孚也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>瑜珈</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pP168p0702b0907" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">梵語也此云相應瑜雲俱切</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>羯邏藍</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pP168p0702b0921" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">梵語也此云凝
<lb ed="P" n="0702b10"/>滑羯居謁切邏朗可切</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>遏蒲曇</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pP168p0702b1013" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">梵語也此云疱遏烏曷切蒲伴伍切</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>蠢
<pb ed="P" xml:id="P168.1581.0703a" n="0703a"/>
<lb ed="P" n="0703a01"/>蠕</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pP168p0703a0102" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">蠢尺允切蠕乳<term rend="no_nor">兖</term>切蠢蠕蟲動貌</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>蠛蠓</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pP168p0703a0117" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">蠛莫結切蠓母總切蠛蠓似<term rend="no_nor">蜹</term>
<lb ed="P" n="0703a02"/>小蟲</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form><term rend="no_nor"><g ref="#CB11215">󲯏</g></term></form><cb:def><p xml:id="pP168p0703a0204" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">輸芮切蟬蛇解皮也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form><term rend="no_nor">蜯</term></form><cb:def><p xml:id="pP168p0703a0213" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">步項切蛤屬</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>蒲盧</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pP168p0703a0220" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">蒲蓬晡切盧籠都切
<lb ed="P" n="0703a03"/>蒲盧蜾<g ref="#CB21926">󵖦</g>也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>土梟</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pP168p0703a0308" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">梟堅堯切土梟鳥名</note>。</p></cb:def></entry></cb:div></cb:div>
